modules.description: This module provides logging functions with tagging, configuration utilities for managing auto-generated IDs and link specifications, and operations for handling bibliographic data through BibTeX parsing and XML citation generation. It works with structured types like `spec`, `auto_ids`, and `wdata`, alongside document trees and buffers, to enable document generation, bibliography integration, and metadata tracking. Specific applications include resolving citation references in XML content, auto-generating document identifiers,
